CalculateField LandUseAlteck2016 landCode landuse( !Ocsol2016! ) PYTHON_9.3 "def landuse(land):
 landuse = {"Corn": 1, "Wheat": 2, "Oats": 3, "Alfalfa": 4, "Beet": 5,
 "Greenery": 6, "Dirt Road": 7, "Grass Road": 8, "Paved Road": 9, "Ditch": 10,
 "Fallow": 11, "Hedge": 12, "Orchard": 13}
 code = landuse.get(land, 0)
 return int(code)"

CalculateField Landuse16_L93 mNumCode "codeFarmerCrop( !Exploitant!, !Ocsol2016! ) " PYTHON_9.3 "def codeFarmerCrop(farmer, ocsol):
 # indexes = [11 , 12, 13, ...]
 farmers = ["Friess", "Speich", "Mahler", "Schmitt", "Burger", "Kopp", "Mathis", "Staath", "Dutt"] # len = 9
 crops = ["Beet", "Corn", "Wheat", "Orchard", "Fallow"]
 # indexes = [91 , 92, 93, ...]
 other_land = ["Greenery", "Grass Road", "Paved Road", "Dirt Road", "Ditch", "Dirt Road" ]# len = 7
 if farmer in farmers:
 final = str(farmers.index(farmer)+11)
 # 11
 if ocsol in crops:
 final += str(crops.index(ocsol)+11) 
 # 1111 (Fries, Beet), 1112 (Friess-Corn), 1115 (Friess-Fallow), 
 # 1212 (Speich-Corn), 
 # 1312 (Mahler-Corn), 
 # 1412 (Schmitt-Corn),
 # 1511 (Burger-Beet), 1513 (Burger-Wheat), 1515 (Burger-Fallow) 
 # 1711 (Mathis-Beet), 
 # 1612 (Kopp-Beet), 
 # 1911 (Dutt-Beet), 1912 (Dutt-Corn)
 else:
 final = "99" # no farmer, 
 if ocsol in other_land:
 final += str(other_land.index(ocsol)+91) ## 9991, 9991, 9993
 else:
 final += "99" # No farmer, no other_land (9999, Not on catchment)
 return int(final)"
